parameters:
"If you're looking for the restroom, it's to the right after you turn at
the entrance."
I was glared at. They probably want to say they don't need any help..

It's a bathtub. It's very big. It looks like more than two people could fit
in it.
It seems to automatically jump up. I was surprised..

"I was told I can do whatever I want until I'm ready, but.. where is the
bathroom?"

→Floor→ "There's a large mat placed on it. I don't know what it's used for,
but it seems like it would be difficult to clean."
→Window→ "It seems like it would be easy to see inside from the outside."
→Chair→ "What is the hollow in the middle for..?"
→Cupboard→ "There seems to be a lot of dishes. Are there a lot of guests?"
→System Kitchen→ "They must cook often. The pots are also large."

→Floor→ "It's neatly organized with few unnecessary items. They must be
trying to keep the space clear."

→Sofa→ "There are many personal belongings around Takumi. He must spend a
lot of time here."
→Speaker→ "Classical music is playing. I wonder if it's always left on."
→Door→ "It's quite thick. If it's for soundproofing, what is it for..?"
(No, what's the point of going outside..)
(No, what's the point of going outside..)
